law.history: Repealed, reenacted, and amended as KRS 194A.125, 2007 Ky. Acts ch. 24, sec. 25, effective June 26, 2007. -- Amended 2006 Ky. Acts ch. 143, sec. 1, effective July 12, 2006. -- Amended 2005 Ky. Acts ch. 85, sec. 37, effective June 20, 2005. -- Amended 2001 Ky. Acts ch. 47, sec. 1, effective June 21, 2001; and ch. 57, sec. 1, effective June 21, 2001. -- Created 2000 Ky. Acts ch. 376, sec. 2, effective July 14, 2000.
